reviewText: Totally love this DVD, made me an instant fan. Going to purchase tickets for the NYC show right now.
Just as funny as the last 6 volumes

Once again these guys have put together a hilarious collection of tapes. As someone who has the other six volumes I can safely say that I've yet to be disappointed by them. If you can see them live, do so! If you can't, the DVDs are the next best option, you won't be disappointed.
